nearby_headings: Note：When the “Wi-Fi on during sleep” option is disabled (default), WiFi will
automatically turn off during system sleep and reconnect upon wakeup,
significantly reducing power consumption. Enabling this option maintains a WiFi
connection during sleep with moderately higher power usage.
